lyrics:
[Verse]
In shadows I wander, lost in disguise
A face you admire but it's all just lies
Sweet melodies hiding the truth inside
With every note, my heart further divides

[Chorus]
My whole life is a lie, a masquerade
Embracing the darkness, the mask never fades
Lost in the echo, the secrets I confide
Behind this facade, my true self abides
